movies.title: Weltraumschiff 1 startet...
movies.plot: Before Television crews and thousands of spectators, Spaceship-1 commanded by Commodore Hardt inventor of the powerful rocket fuel "Neotan-X". Blasts off on the first flight to the Moon.
movies.simplePlot: Before Television crews and thousands of spectators, Spaceship-1 commanded by Commodore Hardt inventor of the powerful rocket fuel "Neotan-X". Blasts off on the first flight to the Moon.

biography.bio: Fritz Reiff was born in 1888. He was an actor, known for La passerelle aux chats (1937), Der siebente Junge (1941) and Rausch einer Nacht (1951). He died on January 18, 1953 in Munich, Bavaria, Germany.
biography.name: Fritz Reiff

biography.bio: Rolf Wernicke is an actor, known for Anna Favetti (1938), A Night in May (1938) and Olympia Part Two: Festival of Beauty (1938).
biography.name: Rolf Wernicke

biography.birthName: Carl Sebastian Martin Wery de Lemans
biography.bio: Carl Wery was born on August 7, 1894 in Trostberg, Germany as Carl Sebastian Martin Wery de Lemans. He was an actor, known for Twenty Brave Men (1960), Das Tor zum Paradies (1949) and Sebastian Kneipp (1958). He was married to Erna Fentsch. He died on March 14, 1975 in Munich, Bavaria, West Germany.
biography.name: Carl Wery
